data.description: Beautiful very well maintained farmhouse with tons to offer inside and out. There have been many updates, while still maintaining the character of the old farmhouse. The electric has been updated to include a new panel & main, newer plumbing, roof, windows and flooring throughout. It has been painted inside as well. The leach field was replaced in Aug 2023 to accommodate the city water. All this gives peace of mind that major items have been recently completed. Along with this, the home and property itself have lots to offer. The property boasts a large yard with tons of space and mature trees with landscaping. There is a large 3 car garage/barn. The home has tons of storage, with extra storage rooms as well as closets. There are 3 large bedrooms upstairs and a 4th downstairs smaller office room. There is a huge laundry room with a half bath on 1st floor by kitchen and another cold storage room behind that. The master has a separate closet room and another storage room behind that as well. This home has a large kitchen, with breakfast nook area and a formal dining room. There is a large living room as well. Close to base and short distance from Watertown. Call today!
